{"tid":1142098,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［又戴帽］選擇原諒會唔會有好結果","createTime":"2019-05-07T01:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T16:51:41.000Z","uid":27974,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b75dfc60839b27fba73bd2c81b96fa1841a9608e","tid":1142098,"uid":27974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T01:02:19.000Z","msg":"初戀比人帽過一次 隔左幾年先敢再拍拖<br />\n<br />\n直到遇到佢 佢對我好專一 對我好好<br />\n<br />\n點知有次唔小心見到佢whatsapp message發現原來佢一直同另一個人曖昩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢認左話對戈個人有好感 維持左曖昩三個幾月 但係只係見過兩次 咩都冇做過 最鐘意嘅都係我<br />\n<br />\n我真係好愛佢 所以原諒左佢 佢都係我面前delete哂同戈個人嘅對話 話唔會再搵佢<br />\n<br />\n戈排我成日唔開心 成日想check住佢會唔會又搵戈個人  但係都冇咁做 唔想段關係變到咁<br />\n<br />\n依家隔左成個月 我地又變番好似以前咁sweet 但係簡唔中諗番起 個心都好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好驚佢突然間會同左第個一齊<br />\n<br />\n有冇人試過原諒完會有好結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb6f9ef12a7e656a72f6c5b85dd91744e880a9f","tid":1142098,"uid":71807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T01:06:33.000Z","msg":"我好似見到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我依家係選擇原諒既階段"},{"pid":"722890f0eb6a2b1aba9c7df841a5c058252e361b","tid":1142098,"uid":52282,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T01:12:39.000Z","msg":"令你失望既人，又點會只令你失望一次呢"},{"pid":"867c33138bbc6837156e0ca12be0acf03841531e","tid":1142098,"uid":91866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T01:16:31.000Z","msg":"你男定女"},{"pid":"b9e2d3ab4b9162cfc27babd3c4cb17aefd6c35cf","tid":1142098,"uid":119372,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T01:58:46.000Z","msg":"一次不忠百次不用 巴打揾定後路啦 實冇好結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bec98702838e4e978dcd08da0b725a3b3c8a409","tid":1142098,"u